summary: You start as elven dominion member, high elf lvl1 Lilith, with first stage of vampirism.
descriptionHtml:
version 2.0
You start now in abandoned hut, where Astrid invite you in Dark Brotherhood.
You have key, and you can go out and don\'t take invite.
You have time to get rid of vampirism.
Map locations now not opened
Spell book now only one - invisibility
LVL still is 1, and now it\'s full clear
Armor now Thalmor robe, boots, and gloves. + elven shield.
Weapons : elven bow, swords, daggers, arrows.

version 0.0.1
You start as elven dominion member, high elf lvl1 Lilith, with first stage of vampirism.
You start at Falian home in Morfal.
You have full elven clean armor set, elven bow, sword, shield, arrows.
Some spell books at bookcase and starter mage robe.
There is no cheat staff in this save
